videos.headline: Cal's Kemery Martin drains a three
videos.description: Leilani McIntosh finds Kemery Martin in transition for a three-pointer to extend the Golden Bears' lead to double-digits.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cal's Kemery Martin drains a three) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cal's Jayda Curry goes off the glass
videos.description: Jayda Curry turns the corner for an athletic lay-in to score early for the Golden Bears.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cal's Jayda Curry goes off the glass) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA's Charisma Osborne beats the buzzer
videos.description: Kiki Rice finds Charisma Osborne to beat the first-quarter buzzer and cut into Cal's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UCLA's Charisma Osborne beats the buzzer) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charisma Osborne nails the tough 3
videos.description: Charisma Osborne nails a tough three to cut the Golden Bears' lead to three.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Charisma Osborne nails the tough 3) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA's Kiki Rice contorts for the layup
videos.description: Gina Conti finds Kiki Rice for an acrobatic and-1 finish.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UCLA's Kiki Rice contorts for the layup) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cal's Kemery Martin goes up and under
videos.description: Kemery Martin attacks the rim and finishes with a smooth reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cal's Kemery Martin goes up and under) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA's Charisma Osbourne with a flashy pass
videos.description: Charisma Osborne finds Lina Sontag with a nice behind-the-back pass to extend the Bruins' lead over Cal.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UCLA's Charisma Osbourne with a flashy pass) 2023/01/15 ESHEET
